[{"Id": 1009996, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "If these statements are said, Satan will say, “Woe to me! All the efforts that I have exerted throughout this year for misleading this person have been failed by the utterance of these statements.” Besides, one who says these words will be testified by the year that he sealed it in a good way.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jab momin is dua ko padhega to shaitaan kahega: “Afsos hai mujh par keh mai ne is saal ke dauraan is shakhs ko gumrah karne ki jitni koshish ki woh is ke in kalemaat (dua) ko adaa karne se bar-baad ho gaye aur is ne apna yeh saal ba-khair o khubi pura kar liya hai.", "UrduDescription": "جب مؤمن یہ دعا پڑھے گا تو شیطان کہے گا :افسوس ہے مجھ پر کہ میں نے اس سال کے دوران اس شخص کو گمراہ کرنے کی جتنی کوشش کی وہ اس کے ان کلمات کے ادا کرنے سے برباد ہو گئی ہے اور اس نے اپنا یہ سال بخیر و خوبی پورا کرلیا ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign