 null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1009995, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, as for any act that I have done in this year from those that You have warned me against doing and You have been displeased with it, I have forgotten it but You have not, and You have called me to repent after I have dared to challenge You, O Allah, I am now praying You to forgive those actions; so, (please) forgive me. As for any action done that draws me near to You, (please) accept it from me and never cut off my hope in You, O All-generous!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Is saal mein jo aisa amal mai ne kiya hai jis se Tu ne mujhe roka hai jo Tuhje na-pasand hai mai usey bhul gaya hu lekin Tu usey nahi bhula aur Tu ne gunah par meri dileri ke baad mujhe taubah ki taraf bulaaya hai. Ay Ma’bood! Mai Tujh se us gunah ki maafi maangta hu, pas mujhe bakhsh de, mera jo amal mujh ko Tere nazdik laane waala hai usey qabool farma aur mai Tujh se jo aas (ummeed) rakhta hu usey na tod ay maher-baan.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! اس سال میں جو ایسا عمل میں نے کیا ہے جس سے تو نے مجھے روکا ہے جو تجھے پسند نہیں میں اسے بھول گیا ہوں لیکن تو اسےنہیں بھولا اور تو نے گناہ پر میری اس دلیری کے بعد مجھے توبہ کی طرف بلایا ہے اے معبود! میں تجھ سے اس گناہ کی معافی مانگتا ہوں پس مجھے بخش دے، میرا جو عمل مجھ کو تیرے نزدیک لانے والا ہے اسے قبول فرما اور میں تجھ سے جو آس رکھتا ہوں اسے نہ توڑ اے مہربان۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ مَا عَمِلْتُ فِيْ هٰذِهِ السَّنَةِ مِنْ عَمَلٍ نَهَيْتَنِيْ عَنْهٗ وَلَمْ تَرْضَهٗ وَنَسِيْتُهٗ وَلَمْ تَنْسَهٗ وَدَعَوْتَنِيْ اِلَى التَّوْبَةِ بَعْدَ اجْتِرَائِيْ عَلَيْكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَاِنِّيْ اَسْتَغْفِرُكَ مِنْهُ فَاغْفِرْ لِيْ وَمَا عَمِلْتُ مِنْ عَمَلٍ يُقَرِّبُنِيْ اِلَيْكَ فَاقْبَلْهُ مِنِّيْ وَلَا تَقْطَعْ رَجَائِيْ مِنْكَ يَا كَرِيْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRed